îíŸ@520194745bcbaa224e34cb719a2da036f6430afa2f5b24d1253996fb608b3b9d⁄ÞTitle: This week in Nushell #204
Path: Nushell
Content:
WindSoilder made redirection improvements: 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9747] make 
``o>``
, 
``e>``
, 
``o+e>``
's target support variables and string interpolation
jntrnr 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9754] fixed capture logic for inner closures
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9695] fixed the input signature of let/mut
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9694] reverted "Fix SIGTTIN handling"
1Kinoti added 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9621] match guards
atahabaki updated 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9750] str-expand: new capability, empty collection item
fdncred set 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9763] history_isolation to false
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9762] changed the default of history.isolation
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9752] handle sqlite tables better by surrounding with brackets
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9749] add range input to par-each
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9731] normalize default_config/env formatting
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9707] allow range as a input_output_type on filter
stormasm 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9745] added a Readme for the crate nu-cmd-extra
amtoine 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9755] added 
``any -> record``
 to 
``metadata``
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9706] allowed 
``into filesize``
 to take tables as input / output
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9676] synced default config / env with default behaviour without any configuration
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9646] changed the output of 
``which``
 to be more explicit
IanManske added 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9736] functions for each 
``Value``
 case
, and fixed 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9730] nushell should be non-interactive if 
``--testbin``
 is supplied
, and fixed 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9693] Do not attempt to take control of terminal in non-interactive mode
sholderbach 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9727] removed underused devdep 
``getset``
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9692] cleaned up tests containing unnecessary 
``cwd:``
 tokens
dmatos2012 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9722] disallowed empty record with empty key,value pairs on ini format
cramt fixed 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9704] removing symlinks on windows
mengsuenyan fixed 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9667] ``detect columns``
 with the flag 
``-c``
nibon7 removed 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9615] the 
``is-root``
 crate
hexavik 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9764] removed unnecessary 
``r#"..."#``
